      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2; addressed implicitly through test conditions and model inputs factors.",
      "rationale": "Formal equivalency mapping between validation experiment inputs and COU inputs is not required at MRL 2. The validation activities used the same operating envelope as the COU, and input parameter correspondence is documented in the simulation plan."
