    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately not-assessed at MRL 2 per the ASME V&V 40-2018 framework. Uncertainty quantification via comprehensive Monte Carlo analysis confirms the relative hemolysis index acceptance criterion (RH < 1) is satisfied across the full input variability space, with the 95th-percentile RH of 0.97 remaining below the threshold. The assessment team concludes that the CFD model has sufficient credibility to support the regulatory decision for the Class II CPB device.",
